						<p>On a third stone built into a wall of the well called Ārettina-bhāvi.</p>						

						<p>1708 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record in Nāgarī characters is composed in Sanskrit verse. Its contents are the same as of the above two epigraphs.</p>						

