<div type="edition" xml:lang="und" rendition="class:nāgarī maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī lakṣmīdhṛsiṁhāya namaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> mārgyagotra tamutpa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nna śrī mahādeksūnunā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> visājīṁpaṁḍiteneyaṁ
<lb n="3"/>kharāmanṛparasaṁsite <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2630 śālivāhana ke <unclear>śā</unclear> 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ke vatsare sarvadhāriṇi <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> mārgaśīrṣe site pakṣe da
<lb n="5" break="no"/>śabhyāṁ guruvāsare <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Āhirbudhnyagace caṁdre suvi
<lb n="6" break="no"/>śālā manoramā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svakaṣṭārjita vittena kṛtākā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>pī bahūdakā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> prītaye śrī naraharerbhūyādācaṁdratāra
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tatpitṛvyasya pauteṇa kṛṣṇājīpaṁḍitena hi
<lb n="9"/>yāktpūrṇā Āvettāvadbāraṁ vāraṁ samaidhitā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> cha <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="10"/>rājā palamahīṁ snigdhāṁ sāpyārāmasusidhaye <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> da <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="11"/>vau me yo vinārvaśrayaṁ dātā bhokā <unclear>sa</unclear> nāralī <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> cha <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

